SKILL_CONTENT='---
name: foundry
description: "Read product specs (apps, PRDs, features) from Assembly Foundry and write back implementation progress. Use when the user mentions PRD, product spec, foundry, features to build, or building from a spec."
allowed-tools: mcp__assembly-foundry__foundry_get_context mcp__assembly-foundry__foundry_get_prd mcp__assembly-foundry__foundry_list_features mcp__assembly-foundry__foundry_update_feature mcp__assembly-foundry__foundry_add_feature mcp__assembly-foundry__foundry_get_architecture mcp__assembly-foundry__foundry_update_architecture mcp__assembly-foundry__foundry_record_session
